msgid ""
"We offer several similar **collections** of ``pixi`` environments for each "
"supported distribution of ``python``. Each environment within a collection "
"belongs to the same `solve-group`_ i.e., environments within the **same** "
"solve-group have their **dependencies resolved at the same time**, which "
"means that all those environments share the exact same dependencies but may "
"also include additional dependencies compatible within the solve-group."
