msgid ""
"The generic :guilabel:`&p&y&3&x&x` solve-group is used here as a convenience"
" to represent each of the different ``python`` distribution solve-groups "
"available, all of which are **identical** in structure and content apart "
"from the specific distribution of ``python`` that they support."
